<p>Thankfully, I have two more summers to "redeem" myself. And better yet, I finally found out how to have this so-called "busy summer" and enjoy it as well. (Ha! I\'ll have my cake and eat it too!)</p>
<p>"How?", you ask.</p>
<p>Well, I genuinely like Biology... so I\'m willingly taking the pre-AP course that my school offers. Basically, I\'m doing something that I actually love during summer so that it won\'t seem like the fun has been sucked out of the sunny-beach days.</p>
